{"tid":710114,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"噚日因大阪地震而冇去大阪 保險公司話一蚊都唔賠","createTime":"2018-06-20T13:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T12:38:16.000Z","uid":108685,"like":2,"dislike":198,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"ef98eb8a653d4e780c2a11a78b05d43767211e6b","tid":710114,"uid":108685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T13:23:09.000Z","msg":"咁我係19號出發即係震後第一日 <br />\n因為安全理由冇去到<br />\n咁我機票酒店就廢晒啦<br />\n打去保險到問竟然一蚊都唔賠<br />\n話如果唔係出發之前保險人出事而去唔到就唔賠<br />\n<br />\n但係我聽朋友話有因地震成功全數賠既例子<br />\n同埋話D保險好古惑 禮貌打去問 佢地就會借D依<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲覺得打過去 問D咩佢地先會認真答我?<br />\n唔望會全數賠 但係一蚊都冇真係令我有D不滿<br />\n<br />\n利申 蘇黎世"},{"pid":"792b85d8b294b7d01030f7d357526a33c75ded34","tid":710114,"uid":30708,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T13:25:49.000Z","msg":"講埋買咗邊份，睇咗條款先有得拗。<br />\n如果人地寫明唔包天災地震，你惡都無用"},{"pid":"25e2d3cbb49273d7b5e5ade53c2ba5f722fa9961","tid":710114,"uid":108685,"like":2,"dislike":75,"score":-73,"quote":{"pid":"792b85d8b294b7d01030f7d357526a33c75ded34","tid":710114,"uid":30708,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T13:25:49.000Z","msg":"講埋買咗邊份，睇咗條款先有得拗。<br />\n如果人地寫明唔包天災地震，你惡都無用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T13:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9okqi4dv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9okqi4dv&h=9ac2c4a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打電話去佢都係照讀返俾我聽<br />\n買咗HKEXPRESS連同既蘇黎世<br />\n<br />\n可能今次真係做咗傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed865b3ddb0f44caa102d83ea155bfa975935802","tid":710114,"uid":29314,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T13:38:14.000Z","msg":"保險除左「人壽」均真之外，乜野都唔想賠架啦。"},{"pid":"ee41981e90d89a033e8c05a1c4fc18b957f4dea0","tid":710114,"uid":30708,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"25e2d3cbb49273d7b5e5ade53c2ba5f722fa9961","tid":710114,"uid":108685,"like":2,"dislike":75,"score":-73,"quote":{"pid":"792b85d8b294b7d01030f7d357526a33c75ded34","t